    <h1>Mutator: Minesweeper</h1>
    <p><img src="/images/mutators/minesweeper.png" alt="" /></p>
    <p>Groups of Widow Mines and Spider Mines are buried throughout the battlefield.</p>
    <table>
        <tr><th align="right">Difficulty points</th><td align="left">6</td></tr>
